title: any idea why I can't create boards? Im above level 5
body: Says I must be at least level 5 but im 22.

replies.body: Your profile might have just needed to sync.  The [syncing tool ](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/fos1aFEB-boards-profile-syncing-tool)is always available just in case!
